      "span_text": "We created voxel-based parametric regression models with the group factor (SCI x healthy controls) as main predictor variable, and age, total intracranial volume (TIV -sum of GM, WM, and CSF tissue classes) and gender as additional variables  in an unpaired two-sample t-test design as implemented in SPM12."
